BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.2 Td (So remember, dear reader: treasures come in many forms.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.2 Td (Some treasures shine like gold. But the most precious treasures have heartbeats.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td (They're the friends who help you through thorny times, carry you across rough waters,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td (light your way in the dark, and cheer you on when you're scared.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.2 Td (Look around you. Your greatest treasures might already be sitting right beside you.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.2 Td (Take care of them. They're worth more than all the gold on Sunset Mountain.) Tj ET
