BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (The Moral of the Story) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 674.2 Td (True Treasure Is the Friends We Make Along the Way) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 646.4 Td (Tiko learned that the most valuable things in life aren't things at all   they're the) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 632.4 Td (people who walk beside us on our journey. Friends who help us, support us, make us laugh,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 618.4 Td (and stand by us when things are hard. Gold might make you rich, but friends make you) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 604.4 Td (wealthy in the ways that really matter   love, laughter, belonging, and joy. Be a good) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 590.4 Td (friend, and you'll always be the richest person in the room.) Tj ET
endstream
